          <span class="px-2 py-1 rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-white/70">Astro</span>
          <span class="px-2 py-1 rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-white/70">Netlify</span>
          <span class="px-2 py-1 rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-white/70">Dev Community</span>
